
This paper describes the questionnaire component of a zzso study to examine the research priorities of zzso care zzso In the first stage focus groups were conducted to determine a list of priorities for future zzso a questionnaire created from these themes was then used in five zzso across East zzso Patients thought that the focus group priorities were important and scored research into emergency care, pain control and helping doctors to understand what patients were saying as most zzso zzso in priority were associated with zzso age and in-patient versus day therapy zzso 

